            <h3>What time does the festival start and end?</h3>
            <p>The festival typically starts at 6:00 PM and ends at 11:00 PM.</p>

            <h3>Are there any age restrictions for the festival?</h3>
            <p>Yes, the festival is open to attendees aged 18 and above. Valid identification may be required for entry.</p>

